Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是在某天放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟森岛学姐去家庭餐厅时发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人脸红心跳的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事发生在圣诞节前几天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 橘 你一副坐立不安的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森岛学姐和我一起到家庭餐厅喝东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我十分感激
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 别因为这点事就感激我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这于我而言可以说是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在成为了现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是难以置信 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:01:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然能够跟学姐喝茶很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却偏偏选中薰打工的店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被她看到这情景的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐决定好要什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 橘能吃甜食的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 一般程度的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要跟我一起吃冻糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冻糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种冻糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想好要点什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的不是薰真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要这一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 应该就是那孩子拿来的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 橘你认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她是我同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们校有学生在这里打工啊 我真不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 被她看到我们单独相处就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我想到一个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我这样藏起来 就不会有人发现你跟我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至于这样做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啦 这样更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 她来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 这是您要的Shining Lovers Parfait
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在想是哪位客人点了如此珍稀的冻糕 原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟什么样的人一同品尝这款面向恋人的冻糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是两个人来的吧 一看发票就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呀 是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐完全在以我取乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不出所料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又怎么样 有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经无语了 那么请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 你可以出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟梅原吃冻糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为学姐藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想知道你会找什么样的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们一起吃Shining Lovers Parfait吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟学姐一起吃的Shining Lovers Parfait很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我却有种怅然若失的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要到圣诞节了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能否跟森岛学姐过一个幸福的圣诞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棚钉 薰篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天薰说她要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打扰她了 直接回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 去书店站着看书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节将至 到时就要跟薰约会去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要买圣诞蛋糕吗 现在接受预订
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的圣诞蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想到书店逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身装束是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就知道啦 当然是圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样 有什么意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在打工 穿成这样也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在家庭餐厅打工了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 这份工作只限这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时薪不错所以我干了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在打多少份工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么多 你应付得来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将要成为新爸爸的人也说了跟你一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前不是说过我不必再打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 那你决定不干了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在考虑中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你看哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没有 只是在想你那猫耳圣诞帽很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 刚才不是看那里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看的是下面的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这样说也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会买的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买最便宜的这个就行了 只需2500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是亏本大优惠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指鉴赏我的圣诞装太便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是亏本大优惠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿得那么单薄 会不会着凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 纯一  用你的身体偿还吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我卖完吧 你想让我在这寒冷的天气中站多久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要买圣诞蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在接受预订
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哦 要买吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要买圣诞蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要买吗  很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小心拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观赏费还真高昂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 就这程度还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:08:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也能尽情观赏薰的圣诞装
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 顺便问问她圣诞节约会想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 现在跟他谈谈圣诞节约会的安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢你 我期待圣诞节的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在圣诞节感冒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多纱江篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是发生在某个12月晚上的琐碎事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天对于少年而言是重要的纪念日 然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然没人在家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 今天是少年的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是回到家里 不仅没看到家人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连生日蛋糕也不见踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感慨要孤零零度过一个寂寞生日的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样把自己关在储物柜里消沉起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别管我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已经被家人以及幸运女神所唾弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年面前站着一位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年似乎仍未被幸运女神唾弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚间来打扰 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 找美也有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 她现在不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学…学…不 我…我是来找教官的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我…祝…祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么知道我今天生日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我问了美也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这是生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:11:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的 是我一点小小的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 外面很冷吧 进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 现在家里没其他人 不能好好招呼你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年一句“家里没有其他人” 在少女脑海中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让其内心怦怦直跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没其他人 没其他人 两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年啊 我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你绝非乘人之危的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以打开看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书 咦 是相册吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:12:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女首次送给少年的生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出人意料的变化球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是内角高球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是远超出少年想像的斜上飞球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 什么啊 哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年在心中呐喊道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是 纱江的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳装照对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是纱江的旗袍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是纱江的护士服照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是纱江迷你裙照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这简直是兴奋的旋窝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是 纱江的睡…睡衣照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年的思想完全暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为了无人能制止的暴走列车——Unstoppable
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为 为什么要送这个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢 我曾向美也打听学长的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她说 学长经常看穿着泳装等服饰的女性写真集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然 然后你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 你那样看着让我很难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得拍得你很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以看 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 一脸埋进少女胸脯的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其反馈 正是温暖少年身心的最好的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些照片是美也拍的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因为她说了解取悦学长的要点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离平安夜还有十天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣夜的女神会对他们微笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:15:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻 老哥会喜欢纱江的礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

